The paper also proposes a unique framework that involves unsupervised learning and generative models, which suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with video data, which suggests that it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with anomaly detection, which suggests that it may also belong to the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category.
